data.description: AMAZING UPGRADED HOME on 1.25 acres in Appaloosa Meadows. Cul-de-sac lot! Free form 18x36 in-ground salt water PebbleTec heated pool with pavers decking built in 2020. 40+gpm private well drilled in 2019. Interior paint, 61/4 inch Colonial baseboard in entire home, and Vintage Lace Porcelain tile planks in entire home except bedrooms in 2022. New KitchenAid appliances (gas range, dishwasher and microwave), tile backsplash and granite counters in 2023. Plantation shutters in entire home, ceiling fans in all rooms, entire home has 10 ft flat ceilings. 2021 New Trane HVAC Air conditioning unit, 2020 New roof, 2019 New paint complete exterior.
